 journalist tutoring a poor child to give a bite against the government.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/shayanroy/everyones-furious-at-aaj-tak-after-this-leaked-video-shows-a|title=Everyone furious at Aaj Tak after this leaked video}}</ref>\n\n==Accolades==\nAccording to a 2006 poll jointly conducted by the [[BBC]] and [[Reuters]], of specific news sources spontaneously mentioned by Indians, Aaj Tak was the most trusted.<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/bsp/hi/pdfs/02_05_06mediatrust.pdf BBC/Reuters/Media Center Poll: Trust in the Media] (pg. 13)</ref>\n\n== Aaj Tak HD==\nOn December 14, 2018, Aaj Tak, launched their first Hindi high-definition channel Aaj Tak HD on TATA Sky Channel 508 owned by Living Media Group.\n\n==See also==\n* [[Living Media]]\n* [[India Today Television]]\n* [[Tez tv]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{official website}}\n\n{{Television news in India}}\n\n[[Category:24-hour television news channels in India]]\n[[Category:India Today Group]]\n[[Category:Hindi-language television channels in India]]\n[[Category:Hindi-language television stations]]\n[[Category:Television channels and stations established in 1999]]\n[[Category:Media in Mumbai]]\n[[Category:Media companies of India]]\n\n\n{{India-media-stub}}\n{{tv-station-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Hindi news channel}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2017}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2017}}\n{{Infobox television channel\n| name = aaj tak\n| logofile = Aaj tak logo.png\n| logosize = 200px\n| logocaption = \n| launch = {{launch date and age|df=yes|2000|12|31}}| network = [[Terrestrial television|Broadcast television]] and online\n| owner = [[Living Media]]\n| picture format = [[16:9]] ([[1080i]], [[news portal]])\n<br> [[16:9]] ([[2160p]] [[4K resolution|4KTV]], [[news portal]])\n| slogan = \"\u0938\u092c\u0938\u0947 \u0924\u0947\u091c\u093c\"<br />(English: 'Fastest ever')\n| share         = 176,711 \n| share as of   = August 2019\n| 